S.FORM: Cameron Bairstow, unu syubay kanasmali miunduay nu Amilika NBA nisakaput, u tabakiay ayaway mimaliay tebanay mimaliay. Cameron Bairstow i 1914 a mihcaan NBA sapapili' mimaliay a kawaw, saka 2 ku uwac atu silsil 49, namapili' tu nu Chicago Bulls putiput. 12 bulad 7 demiad, 1990 a mihca, Cameron Bairstow, miunduay. namakayniay a nasulitan nasakamuan atu natinengan u kasalaylay nu kitakit kanasmail nisakaput mimaliay Lists of National Basketball Association players
